!Block Quotations
Blocks of text can be displayed as quotations:
{{{
<<<
Steve Jobs: "computers are like a bicycle for our minds"
<<<
}}}
Displays as:
<<<
Steve Jobs: "computers are like a bicycle for our minds"
<<<
!Nested Quotations 
Quotes can be displayed on multi-levels:
{{{
> blockquote, level 1
>> blockquote, level 2
>>> blockquote, level 3
}}}
Displays as:
> blockquote, level 1
>> blockquote, level 2
>>> blockquote, level 3
